<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Welcome to CrewControl!</h2>

  <p>Hi <%= @manager.email_address %>,</p>

  <p>Thanks for signing up! Your account <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> is ready to go.</p>

  <p>Here's what you can do next:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Create your first project from the dashboard</li>
    <li>Add crew members and assign them to projects</li>
    <li>Invite team members to collaborate</li>
  </ul>

  <p>You're on the <strong>Free</strong> plan with up to 2 projects. Need more? <%= link_to "View plans", pricing_url %>.</p>

  <p>If you have any questions, just reply to this email.</p>

  <p>— The CrewControl Team</p>
</body>
</html>
